  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK330">
<l>uyiruṭampi ṉīkkiyā reṉpa ceyiruṭampiṟ</l>
<l>cellāttī vāḻkkai yavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(The wise) will say that men of diseased bodies, who live in degradation and in poverty, are those who separated the life from the body of animals (in a former birth).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
